{"tid":997292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太猖狂】佛山狂男自稱經濟壓力大 捉走女童商場3樓掟下再跳樓","createTime":"2019-01-27T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T06:54:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c148608a7fc52da1ff02cfd276dbed43b2bd6e","tid":997292,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"廣東佛山市南海區一個商場，昨日中午有歹徒捉走一名剛從洗手間出來的女童，再將她從3樓扔下後，自己跳樓尋死。2人跌落在商場地庫層，雖有受傷但沒生命危險，目前男子因涉嫌故意殺人罪被警方刑事拘留。<br />\n事發於佛山市南海區的桂城鵬瑞利廣場，36歲姓李男子捉住並抱起一名剛從洗手間走出來的女童，引來不少途人圍觀，李男曾向人群大叫「你們別過來」，之後便將女童從商場3樓拋下，他自己翻過欄杆一躍而下。李與女童都跌落在地庫層一個售賣手機的專櫃上。<br />\n警方事後趕到現場，將李與女童送院，女童頭部、臀部擦傷，需留院治療，而李則多處骨折，沒有生命危險。警方以涉嫌故意殺人罪，將李刑事拘留。警方通報指出，李自稱經濟壓力大，產生輕生念頭，於是獨自在商場3樓徘徊，見到女童從洗手間走出來，便將她抱走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548562357_b577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548562357_b577.jpg&h=da5725ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190127/large/1548562287_fff8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190127%2Flarge%2F1548562287_fff8.jpg&h=8aa5872d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72bb092914bdc414f8148e938769dec85483866b","tid":997292,"uid":30874,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"三樓跳落去都只係擦傷，咩構造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b28d73e9da30693061377c41d063cdddf115f80","tid":997292,"uid":10157,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:01:57.000Z","msg":"200死變2人死其餘輕傷一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b080f16c063154da70d6e550bed5b934b1d65b7","tid":997292,"uid":12143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"三樓 擦傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e3b48e4f8eefce3e38fb9f431a0457f923fc97","tid":997292,"uid":81686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCls"},{"pid":"e3f37a2e126872f35dd99b624d864ce77252e103","tid":997292,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"連登絲打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771679df95b61eb24b614076103d00d57d6e5aaf","tid":997292,"uid":85396,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"原來螞蟻跳樓唔死係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c15aeda79e7eb18fefab73026b31b6a6412fba","tid":997292,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"細路仔骨軟具彈性"},{"pid":"0450bcace5c1c631a29086a3056835a1a4bc229e","tid":997292,"uid":44454,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"佢真係一個好失敗嘅人，殺又唔死，自殺又唔死。"},{"pid":"bbd4425b2387285bd847c3be740c45c7388a9775","tid":997292,"uid":61462,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72bb092914bdc414f8148e938769dec85483866b","tid":997292,"uid":30874,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"三樓跳落去都只係擦傷，咩構造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100024264431187/posts/370893960396082/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100024264431187%2Fposts%2F3708